This ledge is too high... but we have rocket power!
Aim down and shoot at your feet to ROCKET JUMP!

(Shoot: Left mouse button or gamepad right trigger)

property.name: text
property.value: One rocket can't quite make this jump alone...\n\nYou just need an extra little boost to reach the top! Shoot the wall on the way up!

property.name: text
property.value: Woah... this is quite a leap! You'll need the force of two rockets exploding at the same time to clear this gap!

property.name: text
property.value: (You fall faster than rockets fly -- fire one from the top, then rocket jump just before it explodes! Try again!)

property.name: text
property.value: You can jump up small ledges, like this one!\n\n(Jump: W or SPACE keys, or Gamepad button A)

property.name: text
property.value: Continue on through the construction yard!\n\nOh, and ALT+ENTER for fullscreen mode!

property.name: text
property.value: There's 3 hidden coins in each level. You don't need to collect them, but, well, they're collectibles...?!
